	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hmmm, what have you been doing wrong.  I'm level 19 now, been soloing some at every level, now I can kill 2 back to back Sarnaks (even Cons) in the Overthere before I have to med.  Before that I solo'd in Nektalos Forest, East and West Commons, South Ro, Undead in Oasis (levels 15-18).  At these low levels soloing is easy.<br><br>Technique: Root/Nuke, rinse and repeat.  I hit with my mace almost as hard as Warriors at this level, I have the same AC (or close)  I can stun and fear.<br><br>Now I expect to stop soloing soon, I have found a group I like, not because I have too.  But think about it, why be a Cleric if you want to solo, Clerics are a Group Class.  Every Group wants us.  If you want to solo be a Druid.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
